{"lemma":"كِذْبَةٌ","slug":"كِذْبَةٌ","root":"ك.ذ.ب","root_slug":"ك-ذ-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/ك-ذ-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n36774"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%83%D9%90%D8%B0%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a lie"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of كَذَبَ (kaḏaba) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a lie"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/kað.ba/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n36774","headword_ar":"كذّبه","root":"k*b","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tako*iybN","text_ar":"تَكْذِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ki*~aAbN","text_ar":"كِذَّابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tako*ibapN","text_ar":"تَكْذِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tajoribapN","text_ar":"تَجْرِبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.], occurring in the TA, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahabapN","text_ar":"لَهَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pronounced, him a liar; an utterer of falsehood;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a sayer of what was untrue:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he attributed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ascribed, to him lying, untruth, mendacity,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the speaking untruth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb:) and (Msb) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accused him of lying:"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he gave him the lie; said to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"“"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou hast lied,"},{"kind":"text","text":"”"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"&c."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb.) See also 4. ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k*~b biAlA^amori","text_ar":"كذّب بِالاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tako*iybN","text_ar":"تَكْذِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ki*~aAbN","text_ar":"كِذَّابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K: the latter inf. n. of the dial. of El-Yemen: Ks, Fr) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ki*aAbN","text_ar":"كِذَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rejected, disallowed, denied, disacknowledged, disbelieved in,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discredited, the thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anokarahu","text_ar":"اَنْكَرَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k*~bhu","text_ar":"كذّبهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*abahu","text_ar":"كَذَبَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Jel, liii. 11.) Ex."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waka*~abuwA","text_ar":"وَكَذَّبُوا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biA=yaAtinaA ki*~aAbFA","text_ar":"بِا=يَاتِنَا كِذَّابًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And they rejected our signs, with rejection:"},{"kind":"text","text":"Kur, lxxviii. 28]. (S.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*~aba","text_ar":"كَذَّبَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfuw^aAdu maA raA^aY","text_ar":"الفُوَادُ مَا رَاَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aba","text_ar":"كَذَبَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fA^d","text_ar":"فاد"},{"kind":"text","text":", and see 1. ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k*~b Eanohu","text_ar":"كذّب عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He repelled from him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defended him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rad~a Eanohu","text_ar":"رَدَّ عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; namely, a man. (K.) [See exs. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ew~Y","text_ar":"عوّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ew","text_ar":"عو"},{"kind":"text","text":".]       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala","text_ar":"حَمَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"famaA ka*~b","text_ar":"فَمَا كَذّب"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tako*iybN","text_ar":"تَكْذِيبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He charged, and was not cowardly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and did not retreat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hamala vum~a k*~b","text_ar":"حَمَلَ ثُمَّ كذّب"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He charge, and then was cowardly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"did not charge with earnestness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sincerity:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S:) ―         -b2-  or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"falsified the opinion formed of him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made a false charge."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k*~b","text_ar":"كذّب"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eana qironihi","text_ar":"عَنَ قِرْنِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He charged, and then retreated from his adversary."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k*~b AlqitaAla","text_ar":"كذّب القِتَالَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was cowardly in fight."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alt~ako*iybu","text_ar":"التَّكْذِيبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in fighting is the contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlS~idoqu","text_ar":"الصِّدْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k*~b Als~ayora","text_ar":"كذّب السَّيْرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He slackened his pace,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became slow, after giving promise of being quick;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did not proceed in his journey with energy."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA ka*~aba A^ano faEala","text_ar":"مَا كَذَّبَ اَنْ فَعَلَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aA","text_ar":"كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(so in the TA, and in a MS. copy of the K: in the CK, and in two copies of the S,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA ka*aba","text_ar":"مَا كَذَبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) (tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He did not delay to do so:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was not cowardly and weak, and did not delay to do so."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k*~b Eano A^amorK qado A^araAdahu","text_ar":"كذّب عَنْ اَمْرٍ قَدْ اَرَادَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He abstained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"desisted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew back by reason of fear, from a thing that he had desired to do."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"k*~b","text_ar":"كذّب"},{"kind":"text","text":"(and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ka*aba","text_ar":"كَذَبَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA,) (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a wild beast)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"took a run, and then stopped to see what was behind him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whether he were pursued or not."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","Msb","TA","S"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}